{"type":"message","id":"a5c6a26b","parentId":"fb7f8961","timestamp":"2026-03-14T03:35:42.123Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"技能文件创建成功了。现在我应该告诉用户技能已经添加，并简单介绍一下这个技能的内容。","thinkingSignature":"76f13e9a3576b16bddb7d8108123e8d6d0a4fe8399a21647b44e742517fad775"},{"type":"text","text":"已添加 **IT 系统部署技能** ✅\n\n技能位置：`skills/it-deployment/SKILL.md`\n\n**技能内容：**\n\n| 分类 | 覆盖范围 |\n|------|----------|\n| 🐳 容器化 | Docker, Docker Compose, K8s |\n| 🔄 CI/CD | GitHub Actions, Jenkins, GitLab CI |\n| ☁️ 云服务 | AWS, 阿里云, 腾讯云, Vercel |\n| 📊 监控 | Prometheus, Grafana, ELK |\n| 🛠️ 自动化 | Shell, Python, Ansible |\n\n现在我可以帮你处理：\n- 服务器环境配置\n- 网站/应用部署\n- Docker 容器化\n- CI/CD 流水线搭建\n- 云服务上传部署\n\n有具体的部署需求吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":1545,"output":185,"cacheRead":17349,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":19079,"cost":{"input":0.0004635,"output":0.000222,"cacheRead":0.00052047,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00120597}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773459337550}}
{"type":"message","id":"7fb6b2f8","parentId":"a5c6a26b","timestamp":"2026-03-14T03:36:12.425Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b5479347b78b0c49eb11918d4ffd\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_4510d05d4e2eee1944e17801bc935ab9\",\n  \"sender\": \"Roger\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sat 2026-03-14 11:36 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Roger (ou_4510d05d4e2eee1944e17801bc935ab9)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_4510d05d4e2eee1944e17801bc935ab9\",\n  \"name\": \"Roger\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b5479347b78b0c49eb11918d4ffd]\nRoger: 还需要增加openclaw部署技能"}],"timestamp":1773459372422}}
{"type":"message","id":"3baf4637","parentId":"7fb6b2f8","timestamp":"2026-03-14T03:36:22.672Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户想增加 OpenClaw 部署技能。我可以参考现有的技能结构来创建一个新的 SKILL.md 文件。","thinkingSignature":"b88022a992e76861bdd36814fbba112a47e2d1f050d9c4a84d7970713f08cfbb"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_x0x5g0b3d4xh_1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# OpenClaw 部署技能\n\n本技能用于 OpenClaw AI Agent 框架的部署、配置和管理。\n\n## 技能描述\n\n帮助用户完成 OpenClaw 的安装、配置、部署和维护，包括：\n- OpenClaw 核心框架安装\n- Agent 配置与管理\n- 飞书/Discord/Telegram 等平台集成\n- 技能（Skills）安装与配置\n- 网关（Gateway）服务管理\n- 定时任务与心跳配置\n\n## 常用命令\n\n### 安装与启动\n```bash\n# 全局安装\nnpm install -g openclaw\n\n# 查看版本\nopenclaw --version\n\n# 初始化配置\nopenclaw init\n```\n\n### Gateway 管理\n```bash\n# 启动网关\nopenclaw gateway start\n\n# 停止网关\nopenclaw gateway stop\n\n# 重启网关\nopenclaw gateway restart\n\n# 查看状态\nopenclaw gateway status\n```\n\n### Agent 管理\n```bash\n# 创建新 Agent\nopenclaw agent create <agent-name>\n\n# 列出所有 Agent\nopenclaw agent list\n\n# 运行 Agent\nopenclaw agent run <agent-name>\n```\n\n### 日志与调试\n```bash\n# 查看日志\nopenclaw logs\n\n# 调试模式\nopenclaw dev\n```\n\n## 配置文件结构\n\n```\n~/.openclaw/\n├── config.yaml          # 主配置文件\n├── skills/              # 全局技能目录\n├── workspace/          # 工作空间\n│   └── agents/         # Agent 目录\n└── logs/               # 日志文件\n```\n\n## 技能安装\n\n### 本地技能\n```bash\n# 放置到 Agent 目录\n~/.openclaw/workspace/agents/<agent-name>/skills/<skill-name>/SKILL.md\n```\n\n### 全局技能\n```bash\n# 放置到全局目录\n~/.openclaw/skills/<skill-name>/SKILL.md\n```\n\n## 使用场景\n\n当用户要求：\n- \"部署 OpenClaw\"\n- \"安装 OpenClaw\"\n- \"配置飞书集成\"\n- \"添加技能\"\n- \"管理 Agent\"\n\n请激活此技能并提供相应帮助。\n\n## 参考资源\n\n- 官方文档：https://docs.openclaw.ai\n- GitHub：https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw\n- 社区：https://discord.com/invite/clawd\n- 技能中心：https://clawhub.com\n","file_path":"C:\\Users\\73911\\.openclaw\\workspace\\agents\\pv-engineer\\skills\\openclaw-deployment\\SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":36,"output":575,"cacheRead":18125,"cacheWrite":925,"totalTokens":19661,"cost":{"input":0.0000108,"output":0.00069,"cacheRead":0.00054375,"cacheWrite":0.00011099999999999999,"total":0.00135555}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773459372424}}
