{"type":"message","id":"84299fee","parentId":"62203545","timestamp":"2026-03-14T03:36:29.637Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"成功创建了 OpenClaw 部署技能。","thinkingSignature":"1c5af44c2d368e11ce8629ccd96e5612a9cc9b6bdd1742a9b309ed1ab6b1cf10"},{"type":"text","text":"已添加 **OpenClaw 部署技能** ✅\n\n技能位置：`skills/openclaw-deployment/SKILL.md`\n\n**技能内容：**\n\n| 功能模块 | 说明 |\n|----------|------|\n| 🚀 安装启动 | npm 安装、初始化、版本查看 |\n| ⚙️ Gateway 管理 | start/stop/restart/status |\n| 👥 Agent 管理 | create/list/run |\n| 📝 技能安装 | 本地技能 + 全局技能 |\n| 🔧 调试日志 | logs、dev 模式 |\n\n**配置文件结构：**\n```\n~/.openclaw/\n├── config.yaml\n├── skills/\n├── workspace/agents/\n└── logs/\n```\n\n现在我可以帮你：\n- 安装部署 OpenClaw\n- 配置飞书/Discord/Telegram 集成\n- 安装和管理技能\n- 调试和日志排查\n\n还有其他技能需要添加吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":2362,"output":187,"cacheRead":17349,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":19898,"cost":{"input":0.0007086,"output":0.00022439999999999998,"cacheRead":0.00052047,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0014534700000000001}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773459382699}}
