{"type":"message","id":"f0282c6f","parentId":"1502e9ce","timestamp":"2026-03-14T03:37:29.540Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户想要添加一个与 GitHub 交互的技能。我来创建一个 GitHub 交互技能。","thinkingSignature":"56843eb445bd2a4175bb03fb2cbe9d263adf7ce28c741e1c90c2a8c134b9c67a"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_zebuoavi36cw_1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# GitHub 交互技能\n\n本技能用于与 GitHub 仓库进行交互，包括代码推送、拉取、分支管理等操作。\n\n## 技能描述\n\n帮助用户完成 GitHub 相关的操作：\n- 仓库克隆与初始化\n- 代码提交、推送、拉取\n- 分支创建、切换、合并\n- Pull Request 管理\n- GitHub CLI (gh) 命令操作\n- SSH 密钥配置\n\n## 常用命令\n\n### 基础操作\n```bash\n# 克隆仓库\ngit clone git@github.com:username/repo.git\n\n# 初始化新仓库\ngit init\ngit remote add origin git@github.com:username/repo.git\n\n# 提交代码\ngit add .\ngit commit -m \"commit message\"\ngit push -u origin main\n```\n\n### 分支管理\n```bash\n# 创建并切换分支\ngit checkout -b feature-branch\n\n# 切换分支\ngit checkout main\n\n# 查看分支\ngit branch -a\n\n# 合并分支\ngit merge feature-branch\n```\n\n### GitHub CLI (gh)\n```bash\n# 登录 GitHub\ngh auth login\n\n# 创建 Pull Request\ngh pr create --title \"PR标题\" --body \"PR描述\"\n\n# 查看 Pull Request\ngh pr list\ngh pr view <pr-number>\n\n# 审查 Pull Request\ngh pr review <pr-number> --approve\n\n# 合并 Pull Request\ngh pr merge <pr-number>\n```\n\n### 仓库信息\n```bash\n# 查看远程仓库\ngit remote -v\n\n# 查看提交历史\ngit log --oneline -10\n\n# 查看状态\ngit status\n```\n\n## SSH 配置\n\n```bash\n# 生成 SSH 密钥\nssh-keygen -t ed25519 -C \"your_email@example.com\"\n\n# 添加到 SSH agent\neval \"$(ssh-agent -s)\"\nssh-add ~/.ssh/id_ed25519\n\n# 在 GitHub 添加公钥\n# Settings -> SSH and GPG keys -> New SSH key\n```\n\n## 使用场景\n\n当用户要求：\n- \"克隆仓库\"\n- \"推送到 GitHub\"\n- \"创建分支\"\n- \"提交代码\"\n- \"创建 PR\"\n- \"配置 SSH\"\n\n请激活此技能并提供相应帮助。\n\n## 注意事项\n\n- 首次使用需配置 Git 用户信息：\n  ```bash\n  git config --global user.name \"Your Name\"\n  git config --global user.email \"your@email.com\"\n  ```\n- 建议使用 SSH 方式连接，避免每次输入密码\n- 大型仓库可使用 shallow clone：`git clone --depth 1`\n","file_path":"C:\\Users\\73911\\.openclaw\\workspace\\agents\\pv-engineer\\skills\\github-interaction\\SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":36,"output":615,"cacheRead":19048,"cacheWrite":981,"totalTokens":20680,"cost":{"input":0.0000108,"output":0.0007379999999999999,"cacheRead":0.00057144,"cacheWrite":0.00011771999999999999,"total":0.0014379599999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773459431096}}
