{"type":"message","id":"3fd471ab","parentId":"fc4c5e68","timestamp":"2026-03-14T03:37:33.757Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"已成功创建 GitHub 交互技能。","thinkingSignature":"5a5792f20b54ef5fcf32291cf20ece303a06b808874a02289c0c995467626df0"},{"type":"text","text":"已添加 **GitHub 交互技能** ✅\n\n技能位置：`skills/github-interaction/SKILL.md`\n\n**技能内容：**\n\n| 分类 | 功能 |\n|------|------|\n| 📥 基础操作 | clone、init、add、commit、push |\n| 🌿 分支管理 | create、checkout、merge、delete |\n| 🔧 GitHub CLI | pr create、pr review、pr merge |\n| 🔐 SSH 配置 | 密钥生成、agent 配置 |\n\n**常用命令速览：**\n```bash\n# 克隆仓库\ngit clone git@github.com:user/repo.git\n\n# 提交推送\ngit add . && git commit -m \"msg\" && git push\n\n# 创建 PR\ngh pr create --title \"标题\" --body \"描述\"\n```\n\n现在我可以帮你：\n- 仓库克隆和初始化\n- 代码提交和推送\n- 分支操作和合并\n- Pull Request 管理\n- SSH 密钥配置\n\n还有其他技能需要添加吗？😊"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":3381,"output":220,"cacheRead":17349,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":20950,"cost":{"input":0.0010142999999999999,"output":0.00026399999999999997,"cacheRead":0.00052047,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0017987699999999999}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773459449559}}
