{"type":"message","id":"d0830a2f","parentId":"941e92d8","timestamp":"2026-03-14T03:38:59.683Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"完美！现在 pv-engineer 的 skills 目录下有 13 个技能了：\n\n之前有的：\n- feishu-calendar\n\n刚创建的：\n- github-interaction\n- it-deployment\n- openclaw-deployment\n\n从全局安装的：\n- agent-browser\n- feishu-bitable\n- feishu-calendar-operations\n- github-push-backup\n- image-generate\n- multi-agent-feishu-deployment\n- multi-agent-feishu-multi-llm-deployment\n- veadk-go-skills\n- veadk-skills\n- video-generate\n\n让我给用户一个总结。","thinkingSignature":"9c25a02f9d3a0a302b4298840faddacda62d2b9b133e6c3ced9a2f59406ccc96"},{"type":"text","text":"✅ **全部安装完成！**\n\n**已安装的 14 个技能：**\n\n| 技能名称 | 来源 |\n|----------|------|\n| 🤖 agent-browser | 全局 |\n| 📊 feishu-bitable | 全局 |\n| 📅 feishu-calendar | 原有 |\n| 📅 feishu-calendar-operations | 全局 |\n| 🔧 github-interaction | 新建 |\n| 📦 github-push-backup | 全局 |\n| 🖼️ image-generate | 全局 |\n| 💻 it-deployment | 新建 |\n| 🚀 multi-agent-feishu-deployment | 全局 |\n| 🚀 multi-agent-feishu-multi-llm-deployment | 全局 |\n| ☁️ openclaw-deployment | 新建 |\n| ⚡ veadk-go-skills | 全局 |\n| ⚡ veadk-skills | 全局 |\n| 🎬 video-generate | 全局 |\n\n现在 pv-engineer Agent 可以使用这些技能了！还有其他需要添加的吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":5356,"output":341,"cacheRead":17349,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":23046,"cost":{"input":0.0016068,"output":0.00040919999999999997,"cacheRead":0.00052047,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00253647}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773459532522}}
