{"type":"message","id":"8929f6f0","parentId":"5a5724f1","timestamp":"2026-03-14T05:04:21.001Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see the issue - the feishu credentials exist in the config, but they might not be properly initialized. Let me try to check if there's a way to send the file directly. \n\nActually, looking at the config, there are 3 feishu accounts configured:\n- pv-engineer: cli_a920608cfff8dbb6\n- web-developer: cli_a92d03f1b9391bd7  \n- it-engineer: cli_a93e197da0389bc7\n\nThe current session is using \"it-engineer\" but the credentials don't seem to be working. Let me try to switch to a different account or try using the pv-engineer account which is the main one.\n\nActually wait, I should check what account is being used for this conversation. The context shows:\n- chat_id: \"user:ou_4510d05d4e2eee1944e17801bc935ab9\"\n- account_id: \"it-engineer\"\n\nSo it's using it-engineer. The credentials might not be properly loaded. Let me try to directly send the message with the file content, or ask Roger how he wants to receive it.\n\nActually, maybe I should try to create a Feishu document using the pv-engineer credentials. But the current session is bound to it-engineer...\n\nLet me just tell Roger the situation and offer an alternative - maybe I can convert the markdown to a proper format he can download.\n\nActually, let me try one more thing - maybe I can just send the file path and tell him to download it, or copy the content directly in the message.","thinkingSignature":"6916356aac27765f1abfe975587bd655edadab22c6766529c53586a80a59bb7c"},{"type":"text","text":"飞书凭证未正确加载。让我直接复制文件内容发送给你：\n\n---\n\n## 📄 OpenClaw 系统回滚指南\n\n**备份仓库:** https://github.com/WRJ7391117/honor\n\n---\n\n### 方法一：Git 命令回滚\n\n```bash\n# 1. 克隆仓库\ngit clone https://github.com/WRJ7391117/honor.git\n\n# 2. 查看历史\ngit log\n\n# 3. 恢复指定版本\ngit checkout <commit-hash> -- ~/.openclaw/\n```\n\n### 方法二：GitHub 网页操作\n\n1. 打开 https://github.com/WRJ7391117/honor\n2. 点击 **Commits** 查看历史\n3. 选择版本 → **Download ZIP**\n4. 解压覆盖本地目录\n\n---\n\n### 常用命令\n\n| 操作 | 命令 |\n|------|------|\n| 克隆 | `git clone https://github.com/WRJ7391117/honor.git` |\n| 历史 | `git log --oneline` |\n| 恢复 | `git checkout <commit> -- ~/.openclaw/` |\n\n---\n\n⚠️ 注意：`git reset --hard` 会丢失未提交更改，请谨慎使用。\n\n---\n\n文件已保存本地：`C:\\Users\\73911\\.openclaw\\workspace\\agents\\pv-engineer\\OpenClaw回滚指南.md`"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":42243,"output":615,"cacheRead":17349,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":60207,"cost":{"input":0.012672899999999999,"output":0.0007379999999999999,"cacheRead":0.00052047,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.01393137}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773464641893}}
